# warnings

## INEFFECTIVE_DYNAMIC_IMPORT

```text
[INEFFECTIVE_DYNAMIC_IMPORT] foo.js is dynamically imported by main.js but also statically imported by main.js, dynamic import will not move module into another chunk.

```

# Assets

## main.js

```js
// HIDDEN [\0rolldown/runtime.js]
//#region foo.js
var foo_exports = /* @__PURE__ */ __exportAll({ "😈": () => devil });
const devil = "devil";
//#endregion
//#region main.js
const moduleFoo = Promise.resolve().then(() => foo_exports);
//#endregion
export { moduleFoo, devil as "😈" };

```
